text: Teresa Giudice Flaunts Bikini Body in Racy Two-Piece -- See the Pic! by Latifah Muhammad 1:43 PM PDT, March 22, 2017 Playing Teresa Giudice Flaunts Bikini Body in Racy Two-Piece -- See the Pic! Teresa Giudice is "loving" the sun! The Real Housewives of New Jersey star flaunted her insane bikini body in a racy two-piece on Instagram on Wednesday. A post shared by Teresa Giudice (@teresagiudice) on Mar 22, 2017 at 6:40am PDT EXCLUSIVE: Teresa Giudice Opens Up About Husband Joe's Life in Prison: 'He Looks Really Good' The mother of four has been enjoying a girls getaway in Boca Raton, Florida, for her sister-in-law, and RHONJ co-star, Melissa Gorga's, 38th birthday on Tuesday. Fellow RHONJ cast members, Siggy Fligger, and Dolores Catania are also on the trip, which is being filmed for the show's upcoming eighth season. A post shared by Teresa Giudice (@teresagiudice) on Mar 20, 2017 at 2:35pm PDT A post shared by Teresa Giudice (@teresagiudice) on Mar 21, 2017 at 5:15am PDT A post shared by Teresa Giudice (@teresagiudice) on Mar 21, 2017 at 8:01pm PDT A sunny vacay seems to be just what Giudice needs right now. The 44-year-old reality star announced the death of her mother, Antonia Gorga, earlier in the month. She also sent out a touching message thanking fans for their "love and support" during the "extremely difficult time." "My mother was a very cherished part of our family and she'll be deeply missed," Giudice wrote in a touching Instagram post. "Each and every one of your messages of love [and] support are so appreciated. Give her eternal rest O Lord and may your light shine on her forever." See more below.
